// Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2026-1692 — Mass File Rename (incransom)
// Status: stable | Level: high | ID: 9af10143-f185-5aa7-8951-3f9000561347

#event_simpleName=*
| (FilePath = *.encrypted OR FilePath = *.locked OR FilePath = *.ransom)
| table([timestamp, ComputerName])
| limit(1000)
